name: 6 Kings - King Abioye
description:
Sat upon a stool of baobab embellished in gold.
Spears nicked and flecked with time.
Years and years etched in every wrinkle.
A hard man. Unmoved. Unshaken.
A man of regality and nobility.
Only his hand may you touch.
No embrace.
He can see beyond your eyes.
He can hear your soul.
Ancestral wisdom courses through every artery and pore.
The lineage has travelled so far just to reach him.
